<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ill-adv">ill <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪl/    美 /ɪl/  </p>
<p>(worse, worst)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>坏；不利地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>think ill of sb</strong>
把某人往坏处想</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don't speak ill of the dead.
不要说已逝者的坏话。</p></div></div>